OL,3,CLee Anderson: Tory Party 'could have
OL,4,Cgiven me a little more backing'
OL,6,FThe former Tory deputy chairman Lee
OL,7,FAnderson doubled-down on Monday and
OL,8,Fclaimed that the Conservative Party
OL,9,F"could have given him more backing"
OL,10,Frather than suspending the whip.
OL,12,FThe Ashfield MP was suspended over the
OL,13,Fweekend after he claimed "Islamists"
OL,14,Fhad "got control" of London Mayor
OL,15,FSadiq Khan and London.
