OL,3,CLee Anderson: Tory Party 'could have
OL,4,Cgiven me a little more backing'
OL,6,FIn his latest GB News interview on
OL,7,FMonday evening, Mr Anderson again
OL,8,Fdenied that his comments against Khan
OL,9,Fwere racist, adding that he will not
OL,10,Fapologise "while he has breath in his
OL,11,Fbody".
OL,13,FHe said: "Although I didn't directly
OL,14,Fapologise to Mayor Khan - which I'm
OL,15,Fnot going to - not while I have a
OL,16,Fbreath in my body, because the
OL,17,Fcomments I made weren't racist at all.
OL,19,F"They keep banning this word
OL,20,FIslamophobia but nobody can explain
OL,21,Fwhat it really means.
