OL,3,CLee Anderson: Tory Party 'could have
OL,4,Cgiven me a little more backing'
OL,6,FAnderson is a regular commentator on
OL,7,FGB News.
OL,9,FHis comments came after Prime Minister
OL,10,FRishi Sunak called Anderson's remarks
OL,11,F"wrong, ill-judged, and unacceptable".
OL,13,FAnderson admitted that the Prime
OL,14,FMinister's decision to remove the whip
OL,15,Fwas "not an overreaction", but
OL,16,Faffirmed his plans to stand at the
OL,17,Fnext election.
OL,19,FDowning Street has said the Government
OL,20,Fdoes not tolerate "anti-Muslim hatred
OL,21,Fin any form".
