OL,3,CLee Anderson: Tory Party 'could have
OL,4,Cgiven me a little more backing'
OL,6,FThe Prime Minister's spokesman was
OL,7,Fchallenged over his refusal to refer
OL,8,Fspecifically to Islamophobia or anti-
OL,9,FMuslim hatred while condemning
OL,10,Fprejudice more generally.
OL,12,FThe official told reporters: "The PM
OL,13,Fhas been clear that we don't tolerate
OL,14,Fany anti-Muslim hatred in any form and
OL,15,Fwe will combat that and any sort of
OL,16,Fdiscrimination of that kind, as we do
OL,17,Fany racism or prejudice and
OL,18,Fintolerance, wherever it occurs."
